org.apache.archiva.policies

Interface Policy

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DownloadErrorPolicy, DownloadPolicy, PostDownloadPolicy, PreDownloadPolicy
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPolicy, AbstractUpdatePolicy, CachedFailuresPolicy, ChecksumPolicy, PropagateErrorsDownloadPolicy, PropagateErrorsOnUpdateDownloadPolicy, ReleasesPolicy, SnapshotsPolicy

    public interface Policy
    This is a generic interface for policies. Policies define different actions to apply to artifacts during the repository lifecycle, e.g. download, upload, errors.
